{
  "stem": "15578.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 21.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said no, that's not for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm going back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on my way back home, he went at that time to Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we didn't meet each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I did stay in Tomaszow, and he went to Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then he went to Baranovich.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he got arrested.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He wanted to go to Vilna, in order to come to the States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Apparently, you could go from Vilna to the states.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then they send him to Russia, I don't know, to Siberia or what.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there he passed away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was, that was it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was put up posters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And automatically, the Jewish people they start to be together in one place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was almost a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was-- some people that did live outside, and then they had to move in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, except my brother's place was outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we moved in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My older brother, Nojech.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were outside the ghetto until the last day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Until the last--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing I recall, we have to move in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were registered by the Jewish-- no, I recall arbeit, arbeit-- working.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were all registered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], that is right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jewish council.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That they have your-- you're present, whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's never-- they need you, and they have you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there were walls constructed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were constructed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly Ukrainians, from--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean to go in?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One gate was on [INAUDIBLE], that I know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember, there were some other gates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From there, you can go in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you have to go with the Jewish police or some other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Latvian and Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever they named them, I don't know what they--",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
